Cross-Engine Dependencies
SIM integrates with but does not own:
PIE — insight inputs
SIG — signal context
DAT — execution constraints
FLO — financial modeling inputs
GGP — authorization and governance

Completion Criteria
SIM documentation is complete when:
NS-SIM-000 → NS-SIM-014 exist
Scenario outcomes are reproducible
Risk is quantified and explainable
Execution can be blocked by simulation results

